page.title: 16A DAY IN MY LIFE
page.content: ON FRIDAY{12TH.JULY 1985}I GOT UP AT 7-30 AND I HAD BREAKFAST. THEN I HAVE A WASH THEN GOT DRESSED AND WENT TO SCHOOL. I WENT OUT TO PLAY UNTIL IT WAS TIME TO COME IN AT 9AM. WE STARTED WITH ASSEMBLY.AFTER THIS WE STARTED WORK.WE DID SOME MATHEMATICS UNTIL WE WENT OUT TO PLAY AT 10.30. WE CAME IN AT 11.00. THEN WE DO SOME ENGLISH WORK UNTIL 12.00 WHEN WE WENT HOME FOR LUNCH. I CAME BACK AT 1.10.SCHOOL RESTARTED AT 1-15 PM.WE SPENT THE AFTERNOON AT THE PLAYING FIELD DOING ROUNDERS .AT 3.15 SCHOOL FINISHED AND I WENT HOME. I WENT TO THE PLAYING FIELD TO PLAY FOOTBALL WITH MY FRIENDS. I WENT HOME AT 5.00PM. TO HAVE TEA. AFTER TEA I WATCHED A VIDEO CALLED "STAR WARS" THEN I GOT READY TO GO TO BED AT 9-15PM.
